FREEMAN
v.
STATE of NC, et al. 273P17-1 Supreme Court of North Carolina. November 1, 2017 Ms. Jacqueline Freeman, For Freeman, Jacqueline. Mr. Grayson Kelley, Chief Deputy, For State of N.C., et al.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 11th of August 2017 by Petitioner for Petition for Writ of Mandate, Prohibition, Injunction, or Other Appropriate Relief:

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 1st of November 2017."
